ting, Fee  \n........................................................................ 21\nR17-4-412. E x tension of a Special Ignition Interlock Re-\nstricted Driver License: Hearing, Burden of \nProof and Presumptions .. ................................21\nR17-4-413. L i fetime Disqualification Reinstatement ........22\nR17-4-414. Co m mercial Driver License Applicant Driver \nHistory Check; Required Action; Hearing . . ...23\nR17-4-415. R e served .........................................................23\nR17-4-416. R e served .........................................................23\nR17-4-417. R e served .........................................................23\nR17-4-418. R e served .........................................................23\nR17-4-419. R e served .........................................................23\nR17-4-420. Re c odified ......................................................23\nR17-4-421. Re c odified ......................................................23\nR17-4-422. Re c odified ......................................................23\nR17-4-423. Re c odified ......................................................23\nR17-4-424. Re c odified ......................................................24\nR17-4-425. Re c odified ......................................................24\nR17-4-426. Re c odified ......................................................24\nR17-4-427. Re c odified ......................................................24\nR17-4-428. Re c odified ......................................................24\nR17-4-429. R e served .........................................................24\nR17-4-430. R e served .........................................................24\nR17-4-431. R e served .........................................................24\nR17-4-432. R e served .........................................................24\nR17-4-433. R e served .........................................................24\n